# Core Platform Wiki (Phase 1)

Welcome to the Core Platform wiki.

This project is a Core + Modules system inspired by Odoo:
- **Core** provides the runtime (workspace context, app registry, install store, and app runner).
- **Modules/Apps** are optional features registered into the core.
- **Widgets** (Phase 1 concept) are embeddable UI blocks that modules can provide later.

