## Phase 1 Scope
Phase 1 focuses on a working core runtime with:
- App registry
- Local installation (per workspace)
- Enable/disable state
- Workspace app gate/runner
- Control Center dashboard (admin)

No billing, no Firestore, no Stripe enforcement in Phase 1.

